OL,3,CSpecial education needs children
OL,4,C'failed' - Parents protest outside
OL,5,CStormont
OL,7,FChildren in special education in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland are being failed due
OL,9,Fto lack of funding and staff, the
OL,10,Fmother of a child in the sector has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe comments came as scores of parents
OL,14,Fof children in special education took
OL,15,Fpart in a protest at Parliament
OL,16,FBuildings in Belfast calling for
OL,17,Fbetter pay for school workers.
