OL,7,FThey held placards which read phrases
OL,8,Fsuch as "My Child Matters", "You're
OL,9,FPaid, Pay Them", "My Child Is Not A
OL,10,FPawn" and "My Child Is Non-Verbal. I
OL,11,FAm Not", as they walked to the steps
OL,12,Fof Stormont on Monday morning to voice
OL,13,Ftheir frustration.
OL,15,FThe parents were met by a number of
OL,16,FMLAs including Kate Nicholl and Nick
OL,17,FMathison from the Alliance Party and
OL,18,FGerry Carroll from People Before
OL,19,FProfit.
