OL,7,FThe sector has been hit by industrial
OL,8,Faction as staff call for better pay
OL,9,Fand a grading review.
OL,11,FThe parents are calling for the
OL,12,FDepartment of Education to allocate
OL,13,Fthe funding for the workers to end the
OL,14,Faction.
OL,16,FDeborah Maguire from Belfast has a
OL,17,Fseven-year-old child with autism, ADHD
OL,18,Fand severe learning difficulties who
OL,19,Fis non-verbal.
