OL,7,FEducation Minister Paul Givan met with
OL,8,Ftrade unions about the industrial
OL,9,Faction over pay and grading for
OL,10,Fsupport staff.
OL,12,FHe then said the resolution of all
OL,13,Findustrial action is a "priority", and
OL,14,Fhe wants all staff in the sector to be
OL,15,F"paid at a fair level for the job they
OL,16,Fdo", but cautioned there will be
OL,17,F"significant costs".
